<!-- WHAT IS A CUSTOM AI ASSISTANT -->
<section class="section" aria-labelledby="explain-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 id="explain-heading" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">What Is a Custom AI Assistant?</h2>
      <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:1.0625rem; line-height:1.85; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
        A custom AI assistant is a conversational AI system trained specifically on your business's data and configured to behave according to your rules. It knows your products, your pricing, your policies, and your tone of voice. It gives answers that are accurate for your business, not generic answers drawn from the internet.
      </p>
      <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:1.0625rem; line-height:1.85; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
        The fundamental difference from off-the-shelf AI tools is context. A generic AI tool starts every conversation from zero: it doesn't know your company, your customers, or your industry specifics. A custom AI assistant starts from deep familiarity with your business. It has read your documentation, learned your product details, and been instructed on how to handle the situations your team actually encounters.
      </p>
      <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:1.0625rem; line-height:1.85;">
        Depending on what your business needs, a custom AI assistant can be deployed as an internal tool for your team, a customer-facing chatbot on your website or WhatsApp, or a hybrid that serves both audiences with different levels of access. It can be limited to answering questions, or it can be connected to your systems via API so it can look up live data, create records, send messages, and take other actions on behalf of users. As an AI agency in Dubai working with businesses across the UAE, we handle the entire build ourselves, from architecture to deployment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT WE BUILD -->
